			<h1>A scalable navigation and content system.</h1>
			<p>Lazard had 43 regional office sites and needed a consistent way to control and predict the content for each. Coming up with a flexible system that would scale was a primary challenge. I helped design a global content system comprised of modular page templates and a consistent navigation system that helped reduce the maitanance costs for the site.</p>
